'''Fred Kudjo Kuwornu''' (yavutse ku ya 6 Nzeri 1971), ni Umutaliyani , umukinnyi wa filime wo muri [[Gana]],<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/african-film-18-ius-soli-fred-kuwornu/</ref>  producer, uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu akaba n'umwarimu ufite icyicaro i New York . <ref>https://www.filmatique.com/interviews-1/2018/fred-kudjo-kuwornu

</ref> <ref>https://www.bu.edu/european/tag/fred-kudjo-kuwornu/</ref>

Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa documentaire zizwi cyane nka ''Blaxploitalian Imyaka 100 Yirabura muri Sinema y'Ubutaliyani'', ''Imbere ya Buffalo'' na ''18 IUS SOLI'' . Inyandiko ze zivuga ku nsanganyamatsiko za politiki n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage, nk'ivanguramoko, umubano hagati y'amoko, ubudasa, Abanyafurika-Abataliyani ndetse n'irangamuntu ya Diaspora mu Butaliyani na diaspora ya Afurika ku isi. <ref>http://www.weloveitalian.org/kuwornu/</ref> Niwe mutaliyani wambere ukomoka muri Afrika abaye umuyobozi.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Nzeri 1971 i Bologna mu [[Ubutaliyani|Butaliyani]] kwa se uva [[Gana]] na nyina w’umutaliyani. <ref name="fullbio">https://3005e193-e7bd-452d-a040-b74c42987c53.filesusr.com/ugd/6ef997_bf2d0bcabeec4f8f8ffe90c5203e7c74.pdf</ref> Se Perviss Kuwornu akomoka mu mudugudu wo mu karere ka Volta, muri [[Gana]], wageze mu Butaliyani mu 1965 yiga ubuvuzi. <ref name="dotherightfilms">https://www.dotherightfilms.nyc/bio-fred-kuwornu</ref> Se wize ibijyanye no kubaga umutima nubuvuzi rusange nyuma arangiza kaminuza. Nyina Alessandra Giacomelli ni Umuyahudi wo mu [[Butaliyani]] wo muri Bologna. Kuwornu yakuriye i Bologna, nyuma yimukira muri Gana, Ferrara, Roma. <ref name="nuoveradici">https://www.nuoveradici.world/articoli/the-incredible-story-of-fred-kuwornu-film-director-born-and-raised-in-italy-who-now-lives-in-america-and-looks-to-africa/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Amashuri yisumbuye mu Butaliyani no muri Amerika, yabonye impamyabumenyi ya siyanse ya politiki n'itangazamakuru, yakuye muri kaminuza ya Bologna .  Ku myaka 16, Fred Kuwornu atangira ubunararibonye bwe nk'umuvugizi wa Radio Estense, radiyo yo muri Ferrara, bityo anonosora ubuhanga bwe bwo guhanga hamwe n'ishyaka rye rya muzika, mu myaka intsinzi ya Rap n'inzu mu muco w'Ubutaliyani. Umwuga we nka DJ uzakomeza kumyaka 15 iri imbere kumaradiyo atandukanye, nka "Radio Bologna International", na "Radio Jam FM." Ku izina ry'irihimbano “Freddy Ajya mu nzu” akora nka producer wa label Mantra Vibes, amenya imbyino imwe yise “Ifirimbi” (1998) na “Sun Train” (1999). Azahagarika umwuga we wa radio igihe azaba yimukiye i Roma gukora muri sinema na TV<ref>http://www.iitaly.org/magazine/events/reports/article/18-ius-soli-addressing-citizenship-in-modern-day-italy</ref><ref>https://www.coloradocollege.edu/academics/faculty/faculty-by-department.html</ref>.

